---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sustainability"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation sustainability commitment. Environmental stewardship, social impact, and governance. From reversing global warming to terraforming new worlds responsibly."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CORPORATE RESPONSIBILITY
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          SUSTAIN<span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">ABILITY</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-4xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          BUILDING BETTER WORLDS IS NOT JUST OUR MISSION. IT IS OUR RESPONSIBILITY.
          FROM EARTH TO THE OUTER COLONIES, WE ARE COMMITTED TO RESPONSIBLE, SUSTAINABLE OPERATIONS.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- LEGACY -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">OUR LEGACY</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">
              ENVIRONMENTAL LEADERSHIP IS IN OUR <span class="text-[#FFC600]">DNA</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              IN 2016, SIR PETER WEYLAND SUCCESSFULLY REVERSED THE EFFECTS OF GLOBAL WARMING ON EARTH THROUGH PROPRIETARY ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSING TECHNOLOGY. THAT BREAKTHROUGH DID NOT SIMPLY SAVE A PLANET. IT DEFINED THE CHARACTER OF A COMPANY.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              FROM THAT MOMENT FORWARD, ENVIRONMENTAL STEWARDSHIP HAS BEEN INSEPARABLE FROM OUR CORPORATE IDENTITY. WE DO NOT VIEW SUSTAINABILITY AS A COMPLIANCE OBLIGATION. WE VIEW IT AS THE FOUNDATION OF EVERYTHING WE BUILD.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              TODAY, WE APPLY THE SAME TECHNOLOGY AND COMMITMENT THAT HEALED EARTH TO CREATING HABITABLE WORLDS WHERE NONE EXISTED BEFORE. TERRAFORMING IS THE ULTIMATE ACT OF ENVIRONMENTAL CREATION.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">2016</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">GLOBAL WARMING REVERSED</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">PETER WEYLAND'S BREAKTHROUGH</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">47</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">WORLDS MADE HABITABLE</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">THROUGH TERRAFORMING TECHNOLOGY</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">$1.2T</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">ANNUAL SUSTAINABILITY INVESTMENT</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">FY2058</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THREE PILLARS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">ESG FRAMEWORK</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            THREE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PILLARS</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            OUR SUSTAINABILITY STRATEGY IS BUILT ON THREE INTERCONNECTED PILLARS THAT GUIDE
            EVERY DECISION WE MAKE, FROM BOARDROOM STRATEGY TO COLONY OPERATIONS.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-xl font-black">E</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">ENVIRONMENTAL STEWARDSHIP</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              WE CREATE HABITABLE ENVIRONMENTS ON BARREN WORLDS AND PROTECT THE ECOSYSTEMS WE INHERIT. OUR ENVIRONMENTAL PROGRAMS SPAN ATMOSPHERIC MANAGEMENT, BIODIVERSITY PROTECTION, AND RESOURCE EFFICIENCY.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">ATMOSPHERIC RESTORATION AND CREATION</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">CARBON-NEUTRAL EARTH OPERATIONS BY 2060</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">BIODIVERSITY PROGRAMS ON TERRAFORMED WORLDS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">ZERO-WASTE MANUFACTURING INITIATIVES</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/sustainability/terraforming-impact" class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">TERRAFORMING IMPACT &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-xl font-black">S</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">SOCIAL IMPACT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              OUR SOCIAL PROGRAMS INVEST IN EDUCATION, HEALTHCARE, VETERAN EMPLOYMENT, AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT. WE BELIEVE THAT CORPORATE SUCCESS MUST TRANSLATE INTO BROAD SOCIETAL BENEFIT.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">$5B+ IN EDUCATION THROUGH EXPLORERS ACADEMY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">MEDPOD DEPLOYMENT IN UNDERSERVED AREAS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">#1 EMPLOYER OF MILITARY VETERANS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">COLONY COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMS</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/sustainability/community" class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">COMMUNITY IMPACT &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-xl font-black">G</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">GOVERNANCE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              STRONG GOVERNANCE ENSURES THAT OUR SUSTAINABILITY COMMITMENTS ARE MORE THAN WORDS. OUR GOVERNANCE FRAMEWORK PROVIDES ACCOUNTABILITY FROM THE BOARD LEVEL TO EVERY OPERATING FACILITY.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">BOARD-LEVEL ESG OVERSIGHT COMMITTEE</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">EXECUTIVE COMPENSATION TIED TO ESG METRICS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">ANNUAL THIRD-PARTY ESG AUDIT</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">TRANSPARENT REPORTING AND DISCLOSURE</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/investors/corporate-governance" class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">GOVERNANCE &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ESG METRICS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">PERFORMANCE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            ESG METRICS & <span class="text-[#FFC600]">TARGETS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">CARBON EMISSIONS (EARTH OPS)</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">-42%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">VS 2040 BASELINE</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">RENEWABLE ENERGY (EARTH)</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">87%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">TARGET: 100% BY 2060</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">WATER RECYCLING RATE</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">96%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">ACROSS ALL FACILITIES</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">WASTE DIVERSION RATE</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">91%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">TARGET: 95% BY 2061</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">GENDER DIVERSITY (LEADERSHIP)</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">44%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">WOMEN IN SENIOR ROLES</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-2">SAFETY INCIDENT RATE</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">0.31</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">PER 200,000 WORK HOURS</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- UN SDGs -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">ALIGNMENT</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            UN SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT <span class="text-[#FFC600]">GOALS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center">
            WEYLAND-YUTANI'S OPERATIONS DIRECTLY CONTRIBUTE TO SEVEN OF THE UNITED NATIONS SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT GOALS,
            BOTH ON EARTH AND ACROSS OUR COLONIAL NETWORK.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 3:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> GOOD HEALTH AND WELL-BEING</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">MEDPOD TECHNOLOGY DEPLOYED TO 42 JURISDICTIONS. COLONY HEALTHCARE INFRASTRUCTURE.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 4:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> QUALITY EDUCATION</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">EXPLORERS ACADEMY. $5B+ IN EDUCATION INVESTMENT. 250,000 STUDENTS ENROLLED.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 7:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> AFFORDABLE AND CLEAN ENERGY</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">FUSION REACTOR TECHNOLOGY. 87% RENEWABLE ENERGY ON EARTH OPERATIONS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 9:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> INDUSTRY, INNOVATION, INFRASTRUCTURE</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">$6.8T R&D INVESTMENT. COLONY INFRASTRUCTURE. FTL PROPULSION ADVANCEMENT.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 11:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> SUSTAINABLE CITIES AND COMMUNITIES</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">COLONY DEVELOPMENT. SUSTAINABLE HABITAT DESIGN. COMMUNITY INFRASTRUCTURE.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 13:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> CLIMATE ACTION</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSING TECHNOLOGY. CARBON-NEUTRAL TARGETS. CLIMATE REVERSAL HERITAGE.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner md:col-span-2">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">SDG 15:</span>
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase"> LIFE ON LAND</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-2">BIODIVERSITY PROGRAMS ON TERRAFORMED WORLDS. ECOLOGICAL SEEDING. PLANETARY ECOSYSTEM MANAGEMENT.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SUSTAINABILITY REPORT -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-content text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">
              &gt; ANNUAL SUSTAINABILITY REPORT
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              OUR ANNUAL SUSTAINABILITY REPORT PROVIDES COMPREHENSIVE DISCLOSURE OF OUR ESG PERFORMANCE,
              PREPARED IN ACCORDANCE WITH GRI STANDARDS AND TCFD RECOMMENDATIONS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
              <a href="/sustainability/terraforming-impact" class="btn-primary text-sm">TERRAFORMING IMPACT</a>
              <a href="/sustainability/community" class="btn-secondary text-sm">COMMUNITY IMPACT</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
